name: Liquid
tagline: A simple HTML5 territory game based off bursting chambers with fluid.
body: # Liquid Liquid is a simple, small board game. You can play online if you use a new version of Firefox, or a new version of Chrome/Chromium if you enable experimental Javascript features. Otherwise, you can try out our legacy edition.
